Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.07,0:00:11.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:14.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怕你著涼  所以來當你的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:15.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,作為使魔應該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,自從露科亞來了之後一直是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一回到家就黏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我好歹也是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.42,0:00:31.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:34.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我一定要奪回主導權
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:37.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓她明白誰才是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要找出她的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:28.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然還是裸體最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這傢伙在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:35.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還真是討厭穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:37.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這可是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:40.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞  露科亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是主人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,穿上這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧  厭惡到哭著向我道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我穿上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可惡  下一招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:03.95,Kobayashi S2 - Screen 1,,0,0,0,,{\c&H191B30&\3c&H281AE7&\bord3\frz18.3\pos(318.666,634)}黑\N咖\N啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,苦味的東西怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,受不了的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,近鄰的惡犬怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然受不了的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要成為最強的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:27.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果不能完美地控制自己的使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:28.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞的弱點？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我知道個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:37.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,弱點就是那對胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:42.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有那對胸部的話就很難避開攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是在說戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣的話就只有酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:47.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,酒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞不是說她酒量很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:53.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她對酒精的抗性是很好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我不是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是說她嗜酒如命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,平時無懈可擊  但是喝酒的時候是毫無防備的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算下毒也不會被察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那樣會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.49,0:04:07.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說到弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:11.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不如說對於龍來說  人類才是渾身破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:16.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就算掌握了她的弱點  你又能做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:18.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現在的關係不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:27.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞總是到處晃來晃去  取笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把我當成笨蛋  不認可我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:35.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我才想著至少發現她的一個弱點還以顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得她已經認可你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:43.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞很難在一個地方長期逗留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她應該是喜歡才會住在你那的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在這多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我才剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:14.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果你直接問  我就會把弱點告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我最討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是失去容身之處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:25.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我曾經犯下大錯  被驅逐出故土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:27.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那時我非常傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,從那以後我便很害怕長時間待在同一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:37.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但有一個無處容身的孩子  現在找到了容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有點羨慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是你來到我這裡的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是你跟我說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我聽了可是很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我那是指作為使魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:58.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而我卻不成熟配不上你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是很厲害的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只看一眼就能看清你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:16.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你很溫柔  雖然愛逞能但是很努力很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我只要知道這些就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:22.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:26.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我希望你別再把我當成小孩子對待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,翔太  我隨時都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很少見你嘆氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別提了  只是在老家的父母說要來我這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:55.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那法夫納怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:07:00.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我讓他去附近的山裡冒險  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為剛好趕上了新的遊戲大作發售啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就只能把他介紹給你父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:11.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我父母都很直率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一想到他們可能會惹惱法夫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後他就把我的周邊毀掉大半…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:20.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,原來你擔心的是宅物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:22.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:26.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在寶物達成全收集之前  我不能離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,完全沉迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,遊戲已經通關了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不如先休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:37.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可以連續戰鬥數萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:43.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,又沒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓法夫納聽話的辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我覺得和他認識多年的托爾應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:06.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟還欠你之前溫泉旅行企劃的人情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:09.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝  那就快點把方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,靠力量  用力量強行讓他服從
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,除此之外別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:17.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,用力量  讓他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你知道我辦不到還這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真的  除此之外我想不到辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:26.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我與他相遇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是為了爭奪一個洞穴睡覺而大打出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,挺厲害的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,互相認可了對方的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才終於讓他把洞穴分給我一塊地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然是這種相遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:46.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是真的幫不上忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不如你去問問露科亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個大姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她的聯繫方式是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:54.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,被掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有沒有其他的聯絡方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:06.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之前玩遊戲的時候  加了翔太的好友來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要找露科亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:14.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她說要去國外玩  目前不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你碰上什麼麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,如果我幫得上忙的話請說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:21.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我作為魔法使也在不斷鍛鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:28.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幫你的忙也算是修行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是腳踏實地的好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:33.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那傢伙是很可怕的龍對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:40.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,果然比起說服法夫君  還是從父母這邊著手更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我記得他的名字是法夫納吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是在用暱稱叫他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且他也接受了這個稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他說沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:04.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以和他簽訂契約
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:05.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:08.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為他起名而且得到了認可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,契約準備工作已經是基本完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:15.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,魔力之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:21.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我的魔力都注入到這裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,用這個的話  即使是沒有魔力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也可以發動契約的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厲害  翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然後  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能要點報酬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是壽命之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是惡魔才要的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我希望瀧谷你能告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:49.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼才能成為你這樣帥氣的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:52.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還真是令人意外的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這我可沒什麼自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很沒出息的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就這麼約好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,契約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,主從契約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:22.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,魔力之玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只靠這種玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可不會出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:33.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:35.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那至少讓我問問
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:40.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,心氣高傲的你為什麼同意我用暱稱稱呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還不知道有這風險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.21,0:11:44.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你要感謝把這個垃圾小球給你的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他向我提出了條件  要我給他成年人的建議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,成年人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你覺得龍要怎麼樣才能算成年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:04.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然是指從幼年形態轉變為成年形態以後…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:05.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那不過是在身體層面上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對於龍的精神來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,本就沒有兒童和成人之別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:15.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要是生而為龍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:16.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就必須依靠強大的實力
Comment: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/猛武的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:18.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了120pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/信彥的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:19.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了160pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/齊格飛的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對猛武造成了45pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:22.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/花子的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了110pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:23.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/波奇的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了100pt的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.59,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,心理思維也朝著這個方向發展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,父母不會保護孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,之所以出現所謂成年龍與幼年龍的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是因為從接觸人類的龍逐漸增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你明白了嗎  瀧谷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:35.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍在模仿人類
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:40.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,他們也知道這種價值觀有多愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:42.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但依舊還會去追求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在這裡的這群龍也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這不過是扮演人類過家家的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你並不認可這些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這點我還是知道
Comment: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/猛武的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了120pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/信彥的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:57.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了160pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/齊格飛的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對猛武造成了45pt的傷害
Comment: 0,0:12:58.92,0:12:59.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/花子的攻擊
Comment: 0,0:12:59.21,0:12:59.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/對齊格飛造成了110pt的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,堅稱對此愚行毫不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名為小林的人類擊退了終焉帝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我很好奇她們為何做到這種程度也要繼續一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這才加入了這場過家家遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:17.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尋找我要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是允許你用暱稱來稱呼我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:28.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\pos(1418.666,255.889)}獲得固有技能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:28.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\pos(1459.809,683.762)}齊格飛掉落了格拉墨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:28.49,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：格拉墨，北歐神話中齊格飛擊殺惡龍法夫納的寶劍。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,終於出貨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很好  非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,瀧谷  我現在心情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:33.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要是你贏了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就配合你父母好好說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但武力上我怎麼可能打得過你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,誰說要比武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可不會輸的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,區區人類竟敢挑戰我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:50.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但就憑你是不可能戰勝我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不許用必殺連招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,弱小的人類就得不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是覺得我的外表帥才覺得我帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:09.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,男人的帥氣要從塑造外表開始
Comment: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第六話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:18.00,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(350,0)\pos(966.477,598.571)}合緣奇緣（雖然另一半是龍）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:24.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最近我去過河流的交匯處
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:27.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這若是真的  值得誇讚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有照片為證
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拍的很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:37.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蜂須賀你好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那種地方蟲子都能爬過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說什麼  才川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:46.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你可一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還要拍照為證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:52.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是到河流交匯處還要走蠻久的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒關係  我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,給你  康娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:12.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是便當和茶水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是小賣部的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們  托爾大人  伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩得開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:27.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:28.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只有我們兩個人出門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就像成年人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喬吉借給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為了以防萬一可以聯繫上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:45.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,有了這個  拍照作證也沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:52.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蹦蹦跳跳  蹦蹦跳跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只能踩著白色板塊走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,出界就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:17.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:24.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.05,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,上上上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.84,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.80,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,上上上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:34.72,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:45.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:46.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:58.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,涅槃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一  二  三
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學的便當看起來真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是托爾大人做給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:13.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川的看起來也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喬吉很會做飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:19.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不小心掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:33.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我能和康娜同學共用一個筷子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,備用的筷子  借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:41.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝  我會珍惜使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.09,0:17:50.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,喬吉  幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學吃薯條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:54.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:56.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來  康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  你要蛋卷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,現…現在很飽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可惜  雖然是吃我剩的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吃剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:43.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,各種各樣的人都有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼大家都會來河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我喜歡河流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩水的時候很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.15,0:18:54.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩水？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,玩水的康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學真是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪大人忘記展開阻礙認知的結界了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:26.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:27.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,得拍照為證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,康娜同學快讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:32.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但現在重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:48.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,終於到了  康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們到達了河流交匯處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,得趕緊拍張照做證據
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我幫你們拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:08.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:09.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來  康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:20.53,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是從朧塚來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你們走了挺遠的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:28.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們想走到河流交匯的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:34.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡以前改過河道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:37.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼要改河道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:43.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為了預防洪水  還有利於糧食種植
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:45.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回去要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:48.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也會改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:21:01.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那肯定會變得更加可愛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:04.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川也會改變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:08.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒錯  肯定會變成一個好女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:21.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,河裡面有怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.88,0:21:29.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能說得再詳細點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,它有這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在河裡玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:33.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說是吧康娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,才川  那是CG
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:38.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:41.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就是AR囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.61,0:21:43.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看  果然就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,CG？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:48.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是CG
